Class TextFileDataset

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<FImage>, Map<String,ListDataset<FImage>>, Dataset<FImage>, GroupedDataset<String,ListDataset<FImage>,FImage>

    public class TextFileDataset
extends MapBackedDataset<String,ListDataset<FImage>,FImage>
    A simple dataset of people and their images, backed by a text file with the following format: 
      personA,/path/to/image.jpg
  personA,/path/to/image1.jpg
  personB,/path/to/image2.jpg
  ...
    The default separator is a comma, but is user controllable.

    In addition to allowing datasets to be read from a file, this implementation also allows datasets to be created or appended to through the add(String, File) method.

    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
